{
  "texts": [
    "Herein, two models AnnoPRO UMAP and AnnoPRO PCA were thus constructed based on UMAP and PCA, respectively (the procedure for model construction and evaluation is described above).",
    "As shown in Additional file 1: Fig.",
    "S2, the performances (assessed by F max and AUPRC) of these models are roughly the same across three GO classes (BP, CC, MF).",
    "Particularly, AnnoPRO UMAP showed a slightly better predictive performance compared with AnnoPRO PCA (0.6 ~ 1.9% for F max; 1.4 ~ 2.1% for AUPRC).",
    "All in all, although concerns were raised about the limitations of UMAP [43], the performance evaluation conducted in this study showed that the application of different dimensionality reduction methods (UMAP vs PCA) might not significantly alter the performance."
  ]
}